      "status": "todo",
      "title": "Suppress Mac watcher degraded warnings during active retry",
      "description": "Queue watcher health reports a warning for degraded state while the watcher still has a scheduled retry. Goal: render active self-healing as neutral/informational status and reserve warning/error severity for exhausted or operator-action states.",
